OL,3,CWhat do we know so far about the
OL,4,Ccruise ship hantavirus outbreak?
OL,6,FThree passengers have died and a
OL,7,FBritish crew member remains seriously
OL,8,Fill after an outbreak of hantavirus
OL,9,Finfection onboard a cruise ship.
OL,11,FA total of seven suspected cases have
OL,12,Fbeen identified. Of the cases
OL,13,Freported, one patient is critically
OL,14,Fill, three patients report mild
OL,15,Fsymptoms, and three patients have died.
OL,17,FThe World Health Organisation (WHO) is
OL,18,Fworking to establish the cause of the
OL,19,Foutbreak of the virus that is usually
OL,20,Fspread through rodent contact.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
