OL,3,CWhat do we know so far about the
OL,4,Ccruise ship hantavirus outbreak?
OL,6,FSeveral uncertainties remain. Here's
OL,7,Fwhat is known about the fatal outbreak
OL,8,Fso far.
OL,10,FWhen did the outbreak begin?
OL,12,FThe WHO has identified seven cases,
OL,13,Fincluding two laboratory-confirmed
OL,14,Fhantavirus infections and five
OL,15,Fsuspected cases, between 6 and 28
OL,16,FApril.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778054737
OL,3,CWhat do we know so far about the
OL,4,Ccruise ship hantavirus outbreak?
OL,6,FExperts say the incubation period
OL,7,Fbetween infection and symptoms can be
OL,8,Fup to eight weeks, so the precise
OL,9,Fmoment of infection onboard the ship
OL,10,Fremains unknown.
OL,12,FWhat is the source of the infection?
OL,14,FThe precise source of infection aboard
OL,15,Fship hasn't been pinpointed, and the
OL,16,Ffull extent of person-to-person
OL,17,Ftransmission remains unclear.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
