OL,3,CWhat do we know so far about the
OL,4,Ccruise ship hantavirus outbreak?
OL,6,FOnly limited human-to-human spread has
OL,7,Fbeen documented previously with the
OL,8,FAndes virus ` the most common cause of
OL,9,Fhantavirus pulmonary syndrome (HPS) in
OL,10,FSouth America.
OL,12,FThe incubation period and disease
OL,13,Fprogression rates of this outbreak
OL,14,Fwarrant careful monitoring.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
