OL,3,CWhat do we know so far about the
OL,4,Ccruise ship hantavirus outbreak?
OL,6,FGroup leader and senior lecturer at
OL,7,Fthe MRC-University of Glasgow Centre
OL,8,Ffor Virus Research, Dr Benjamin
OL,9,FBrennan, said that as hantavirus
OL,10,Ftypically spreads through rodent
OL,11,Fcontact, "its appearance in a cruise
OL,12,Fship environment "raises questions
OL,13,Fabout contamination pathways".
OL,15,FWhat is the South America travel
OL,16,Fhistory connection?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
