OL,3,CWhat do we know so far about the
OL,4,Ccruise ship hantavirus outbreak?
OL,6,FThe ship left Ushuaia in southern
OL,7,FArgentina on April 1, according to
OL,8,FArgentine provincial authorities.
OL,9,FHealth officials there said they
OL,10,Fconfirmed no passengers had hantavirus
OL,11,Fsymptoms when the Hondius departed.
OL,13,FBut because symptoms can appear up to
OL,14,Feight weeks after exposure, "the
OL,15,Fpassengers could have been incubating
OL,16,Fthe disease if they acquired it within
OL,17,Fthe country or elsewhere in the
OL,18,Fworld," Juan Facundo Petrina, director
OL,19,Fof epidemiology for Tierra del Fuego
OL,20,Fprovince, told AP in an interview from
OL,21,FUshuaia.
OL,26,@vD@]OUzD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
