PN,31707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778054737
OL,3,CWhat do we know so far about the
OL,4,Ccruise ship hantavirus outbreak?
OL,6,FHe noted that the province has not
OL,7,Fhistorically recorded hantavirus
OL,8,Fcases, but outbreaks have occurred in
OL,9,Fother Argentine provinces, leading to
OL,10,F28 deaths nationwide last year,
OL,11,Faccording to the health ministry.
OL,13,F"Cases 1 and 2 travelled in South
OL,14,FAmerica, including Argentina, before
OL,15,Fboarding the cruise ship," Dr Brennan
OL,16,Fsaid, a piece of epidemiological
OL,17,Finformation he described as "crucial"
OL,18,Fas it "suggests the infection was
OL,19,Facquired in a hantavirus-endemic
OL,20,Fregion and brought aboard, rather than
OL,21,Foriginating from shipboard conditions".
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778054737
OL,3,CWhat do we know so far about the
OL,4,Ccruise ship hantavirus outbreak?
OL,6,F"Argentina is where the Andes virus
OL,7,Fcirculates, so identifying which virus
OL,8,Fstrain is responsible is essential for
OL,9,Fassessing the ongoing risks associated
OL,10,Fwith the outbreak," he said.
OL,12,FDr Brennan continued: "The travel
OL,13,Fhistories of other passengers and crew
OL,14,Fmembers are still being investigated,
OL,15,Fso it remains uncertain whether
OL,16,Fadditional individuals may have had
OL,17,Fexposure to hantavirus sources in
OL,18,Fendemic areas before boarding or
OL,19,Fduring port stops.
OL,26,@tD@WOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778054737
OL,3,CWhat do we know so far about the
OL,4,Ccruise ship hantavirus outbreak?
OL,6,F"However, most passengers and crew
OL,7,Fwill have been in close quarters
OL,8,Fthroughout the virus incubation
OL,9,Fperiod, leading to the potential for
OL,10,Fsecondary cases to occur."
OL,12,FDr Michael Head, senior research
OL,13,Ffellow in global health at the
OL,14,FUniversity of Southampton, said that
OL,15,Fas two of the cases had travelled in
OL,16,FSouth America before boarding the
OL,17,Fvessel, it indicated "that those cases
OL,18,Fwere likely infected by an
OL,19,Fenvironmental exposure at that point".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,318,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31710
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778054737
OL,3,CWhat do we know so far about the
OL,4,Ccruise ship hantavirus outbreak?
OL,6,F"The incubation period from initial
OL,7,Finfection to symptoms can be several
OL,8,Fweeks, so it does fit within the
OL,9,Ftimelines presented," he said.
OL,11,FBut he cautioned against assuming it
OL,12,Fwas linked to the Andes strain as
OL,13,Flaboratory tests continue.
OL,15,F"There have been documented cases of
OL,16,Fhuman-to-human transmission from the
OL,17,FAndes strain, specifically within
OL,18,FArgentina," he said.
OL,26,@zD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
