PN,31711
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F317A1778054737
OL,3,CWhat do we know so far about the
OL,4,Ccruise ship hantavirus outbreak?
OL,6,F"In one outbreak, there was a single
OL,7,Fenvironmental exposure to rodents and
OL,8,Fthree symptomatic patients then
OL,9,Finfected others at crowded social
OL,10,Fevents, resulting in 34 cases and 11
OL,11,Fdeaths.
OL,13,F"Here, on the MV Hondius, we do not
OL,14,Fyet know if there is human-to-human
OL,15,Ftransmission. Knowledge of the strain
OL,16,Fis therefore important to
OL,17,Funderstanding the risks to the
OL,18,Fpassengers who are still on board."
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
