OL,3,CWhat do we know so far about the
OL,4,Ccruise ship hantavirus outbreak?
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FWhat is being done to reduce the
OL,12,Fspread?
OL,14,FDr Brennan said rapid isolation,
OL,15,Fmedical evacuation and contact tracing
OL,16,Famong the more than 140 passengers and
OL,17,Fup to 70 crew were the priority and
OL,18,Fkey to reducing the spread.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
