OL,3,CWhat do we know so far about the
OL,4,Ccruise ship hantavirus outbreak?
OL,6,FSouth Africa's National Institute for
OL,7,FCommunicable Diseases was conducting
OL,8,Fcontact tracing to identify whether
OL,9,Fpeople were exposed to infected cruise
OL,10,Fpassengers.
OL,12,FThe 69-year-old woman who died was
OL,13,Ftrying to catch a flight home to the
OL,14,FNetherlands at Johannesburg's main
OL,15,Finternational airport, one of Africa's
OL,16,Fbusiest, when she collapsed.
OL,18,FHantavirus has no specific treatment
OL,19,For cure, but early medical attention
OL,20,Fcan increase chances of survival.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
