OL,3,CWhat do we know so far about the
OL,4,Ccruise ship hantavirus outbreak?
OL,6,FAre there British nationals on board?
OL,8,FSome 19 British nationals were listed
OL,9,Fas passengers on the ship, which was
OL,10,Fsailing from Argentina to Cape Verde,
OL,11,Fwith four British crew members.
OL,13,FA British crew member who became
OL,14,Funwell after a suspected hantavirus
OL,15,Foutbreak on a cruise ship in the
OL,16,FAtlantic Ocean is to be medically
OL,17,Fevacuated, officials have said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
