OL,3,CWhat do we know so far about the
OL,4,Ccruise ship hantavirus outbreak?
OL,6,FA British passenger struck down by
OL,7,Fhantavirus is "understood to be
OL,8,Fimproving". The passenger of the Dutch-
OL,9,Fflagged cruise ship MV Hondius was
OL,10,Fmedically evacuated on April 27 to
OL,11,FJohannesburg and remains in intensive
OL,12,Fcare.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
